            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/18/IMG-7202_0.jpg?VersionId=AA66tzGGMU_tbXbAfk760oRTUdi8Xzmi&amp;itok=nmjz0owd" title="鸿海集团创办人郭台铭星期二（4月18日）在记者会上表明，对国民党征召程序深信不疑。（庄慧良摄）" alt="鸿海集团创办人郭台铭星期二（4月18日）在记者会上表明，对国民党征召程序深信不疑。（庄慧良摄）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/18/IMG-7202_0.jpg?VersionId=AA66tzGGMU_tbXbAfk760oRTUdi8Xzmi&amp;itok=nmjz0owd" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
